# Loc
# "best" (default) - Automatically chooses the best position.
# "upper right" / "upper left" / "lower right" / "lower left"
# "center" / "center right" / "center left"
# frameon=False : Remove the legend frame
# framealpha=0.5  Set frame transparency: # 0 (fully transparent) to 1 (opaque)

plt.plot(Salary[0],c='Green',ls='--',marker='o',ms=5,label=Players[0]) 
plt.plot(Salary[1],c='Blue',ls='-',marker='d',ms=5,label=Players[1]) 
plt.plot(Salary[2],c='Purple',ls='-.',marker='^',ms=5,label=Players[2]) 
plt.plot(Salary[3],c='Red',ls='-.',marker='^',ms=5,label=Players[3]) 
plt.legend(loc="best",title="Legend Title",fontsize=12,frameon=False,framealpha=0.5)
plt.xticks(list(range(0,10)),Seasons,rotation='vertical')
plt.show()
